{"tid":27950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州中學生：好慘，成間學校得我一個講廣東話","createTime":"2016-12-07T15:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T12:21:16.000Z","uid":22675,"like":68,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bcb08cb632b24cb69fd7e0d2a4514ec95aa491a8","tid":27950,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:48:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/4378868155?pn=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F4378868155%3Fpn%3D2&d=X%2BSTMYEMSAHrUNu%2FG3a630sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=9a5e77e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://tieba.baidu.com/p/4378868155?pn=2</a><br />\n<br />\n本人高二。。。由細到大都系廣州讀書。。。小學初中系天河區讀，高中果斷考到越秀老城區。<br />\n14年高一入學時仲有猴多同學講粵語，同班果滴就算講不標準都會跟住我地講。但系去年15年見到果滴新高一入學，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>身邊經過果滴高一生竟然聽唔到幾句粵語</strong></span></span>。。。殊不知，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>我地校歌系用粵語唱的。跟住依家有滴大型活動要唱校歌時就聽到滴高一生講滴咩&ldquo;不會唱啊。&rdquo;&ldquo;聽不懂。&rdquo;甚至乎有滴過激的口口聲講要將校歌改為普通話</strong></span></span>。<br />\n我真系唔明。而且非常之不爽央視將粵語定義為方言。憑咩？你講粵語冇自己文化，冇自己文字，冇自己發源地。系南蠻之地的方言。唔冇講到普通話真系大塞甘！雖然我只系一個高中生，但系我決不允許我屋企門口滴文化被邊緣化。我初中果間學校，根本就冇粵語社（果陣維護粵語的思想仲冇依家甘嚴重）只有京劇社。可能因為系天河讀小學同初中，外省人超多！系超多！！所以一個班45個人，數埋都可能得5-7個識講。有好多人，識講，但系唔講。點解？曾經系高中隔離果間雲吞面度食午飯，隔離臺坐住一家人。爸爸媽咪講住順到不得了的粵語，但系個仔仔一問問題就轉用普通話來回答。仔仔都系講普通話的。甘樣算咩行為？唔通你認為，粵語唔應該系自己屋企門口發展？距唔重要？比普通話低個檔次？<br />\n以上真系我一直隱藏在心裏面滴話。我猴心疼點解自己的語言要被邊緣化。我決不允許，甘樣的情況在我屋企門口&mdash;&mdash;廣州。發生。距唔系你地北方人口口相傳的方言，距系一門語言。你地冇資格定義距為方言。而且我個人認為，粵語同其他被央視定義為方言的語種不同。其他果滴（唔敢講全部，只能講大部分）猴多都系以普通話為基調。意思就系講，我覺得距地大部分都系以國語為基調再加上自己當地講話的習慣，形成一種方言。果滴就真系感覺系方言咯，都系普通話的音。<br />\n我唔希望，都唔想見到，屋企門口的語言&mdash;&mdash;粵語。被央視邊緣化。國語是方便全中國人學習。只因它只有四個音。平平仄仄。而我們的粵語有九個音，哪怕從小被灌輸&ldquo;唐詩宋詞是用普通話來讀的&rdquo;這種思想。但我還是會用粵語把在學的古文古詩讀一遍。儘管我讀得很拗口。但我中意粵語，我都唔會放棄距。永遠。<br />\n以識講粵語自豪！"},{"pid":"0d72eb7b12b054d25912767ab473067497e1b3e1","tid":27950,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d15851b7ff549f19810e045c7080a24228a1c4","tid":27950,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:56:01.000Z","msg":"香港都就來咁<br />\n近幾年出街見好多學生講普通話<br />\n可能我住係窮撚地區"},{"pid":"3e414318901dfcfe3430e137042fa5e2ab04ee06","tid":27950,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:57:22.000Z","msg":"雖然好多5P字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好在有人有呢份心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5b166a8a0fe4fe4d6aaab748ffd15452f75863","tid":27950,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:57:34.000Z","msg":"兩邊走你都好忙姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c997d93352ac39c2db4734ee5324559b12629aee","tid":27950,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:58:57.000Z","msg":"屌 香港唔少中學都用普通話唱校歌<br />\n反而大陸都仲有廣東話"},{"pid":"fc42597694e614963ce30126b2adbb0190a15ff4","tid":27950,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T15:59:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩邊走你都好忙姐</blockquote><br />\n兩邊走?"},{"pid":"e09fdc437c202dd9517100d1a319943d04a51965","tid":27950,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>兩邊走你都好忙姐</blockquote><br />\n兩邊走?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n高登lihkg"},{"pid":"d4627e28c9b7cf9f994f26e0b0bd7a0264a00d46","tid":27950,"uid":21024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:09:43.000Z","msg":"大陸親戚d仔女已經唔識講廣東話<br />\n學校講廣東話會比人鬧 全部都識聽唔識講<br />\n中共要滅廣東話真係幾十年就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e802f21955dc467820d7478af680356de1ed1ae","tid":27950,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:16:25.000Z","msg":"明日香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5bec3e6dc96af6b7d01152bd3907e7794fb128","tid":27950,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:25:58.000Z","msg":"系你老母"},{"pid":"258f227073973bd72842d83fcc7a6ad17c10c335","tid":27950,"uid":24739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:28:40.000Z","msg":"真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b456d38e12aaf3802f5c0972b739d8c3f7bd32ce","tid":27950,"uid":26553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想同佢瘋狂咁講廣東話"},{"pid":"a5be0d4239c0ae70800ded7c1b060c0f81764560","tid":27950,"uid":38286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:35:00.000Z","msg":"係網吧打機都有好撚多中學生係到講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b845164a032944db1aee7f77a084351988eda44","tid":27950,"uid":5715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481b508023fe9f33d0ace5040be9673e19edee95","tid":27950,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:41:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>兩邊走你都好忙姐</blockquote><br />\n兩邊走?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n高登lihkg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔去高登點抄post"},{"pid":"92bcd22cba047e1f98a63b88691de381f78677c1","tid":27950,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"係咪執信/培正etc果d港中分校都係同源嘅學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0833abb9eac1d8c1adb87436c5198f02816029","tid":27950,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T17:13:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港都就來咁<br />\n<br />\n近幾年出街見好多學生講普通話<br />\n<br />\n可能我住係窮撚地區</blockquote><br />\n所以我一向提倡要大力恥笑啲細蚊仔講蝗語，係蝗蟲<br />\n要恥笑到佢哋喊嗰隻，唔可以留手<br />\n有陰影就自然唔講"},{"pid":"9a62b3ad5e4ae713099565e9345d07eb007526bb","tid":27950,"uid":57269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:06:52.000Z","msg":"滴(啲)個音好有廣州口音，好地道嘅味道😂"},{"pid":"bb9c476799efd142fc9ef3973a6e4d208fb84bd6","tid":27950,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />細佬班群d人用普通話講野<br />\n我細佬又唔屌鳩佢地反而就返佢地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16caf755bc5f557dbac79fca6b2d8b84ac9df5a","tid":27950,"uid":59626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:45:38.000Z","msg":"同胞不用怕還有黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff7dfd7eff9e0a5c96cc6331699987602082abf","tid":27950,"uid":33653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T18:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸親戚d仔女已經唔識講廣東話<br />\n學校講廣東話會比人鬧 全部都識聽唔識講<br />\n中共要滅廣東話真係幾十年就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n死淨班老中，我做訂房都試過，有廣州老母訂房，用廣東話交談時，佢個幾歲仔係到用匪語係咁屌佢老母講廣東話。( 心諗做人老母甚艱難 )"},{"pid":"cfd10b9c6edaccf65c12764edb0d5a9b26473d08","tid":27950,"uid":2707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:09:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸親戚d仔女已經唔識講廣東話<br />\n學校講廣東話會比人鬧 全部都識聽唔識講<br />\n中共要滅廣東話真係幾十年就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n華人個底根本就垃撚圾<br />\n上面係優秀文明都話，又唔係，都畀人同化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a95c87f1da31ab32e565ad13781012ecd32bb8b","tid":27950,"uid":34037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9073fe7d5e0d3a57642b8733c27a5df2bc75b1","tid":27950,"uid":22387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:23:42.000Z","msg":"我係旺角區返工<br />\n發現個堆中學好多學生都講普通話<br />\n仲要係好平常咁 <br />\n諗緊家下會唔會年輕一代已經有一大部分人係大陸哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d67a575365bdbec1517d3f78ad0287510a68886","tid":27950,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:35:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然好多5P字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好在有人有呢份心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根本用5p字最多嘅就係支那豬"},{"pid":"f6dcdd4ccdc6905cc3b268321fe20849548dd6a8","tid":27950,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大陸親戚d仔女已經唔識講廣東話<br />\n學校講廣東話會比人鬧 全部都識聽唔識講<br />\n中共要滅廣東話真係幾十年就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n華人個底根本就垃撚圾<br />\n上面係優秀文明都話，又唔係，都畀人同化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n崇優就話 <br />\n支國呢d垃圾文化，社會觀 就去學<br />\n<br />\n簡體字 本來是比唔識破的人用 提高識字率<br />\n普通話更受支那成日講的北方遊牧民族的影響<br />\n<br />\n到今日 究竟咩做文明人 說文明話<br />\n班支那人簡直忽上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63140218ec27bf272be31d5c95d0bd4af48b964b","tid":27950,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係旺角區返工<br />\n發現個堆中學好多學生都講普通話<br />\n仲要係好平常咁 <br />\n諗緊家下會唔會年輕一代已經有一大部分人係大陸哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係住旺角<br />\n我想講幾年前我仲係旺角讀書果陣已經係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，低我兩屆(果班應該97年出世)真係唔少明目張膽係學校普通話傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諸聖仲誇張(係開你地學校名，吹咩)，佢地放飯出黎果陣，行過基本上聽倒佢地全部都係講普通話(尤其係d女仔)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121a6ef6264f8e29519bf0a8cf7da0fe4b94ce48","tid":27950,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大陸親戚d仔女已經唔識講廣東話<br />\n學校講廣東話會比人鬧 全部都識聽唔識講<br />\n中共要滅廣東話真係幾十年就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n華人個底根本就垃撚圾<br />\n上面係優秀文明都話，又唔係，都畀人同化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n崇優就話 <br />\n支國呢d垃圾文化，社會觀 就去學<br />\n<br />\n簡體字 本來是比唔識破的人用 提高識字率<br />\n普通話更受支那成日講的北方遊牧民族的影響<br />\n<br />\n到今日 究竟咩做文明人 說文明話<br />\n班支那人簡直忽上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過班支那賤畜 全部都賤骨頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個嘉定三屠 揚州十日<br />\n留髮不留頭 留頭不番髮<br />\n大玩文字獄<br />\n<br />\n的政權 究竟可以拍一大堆電視劇幫佢吹噓"},{"pid":"e80e711615fd2f028dd712cba972c465fa35bb0c","tid":27950,"uid":11907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:58:06.000Z","msg":"其實香港好快都會係咁，依家班細路個個普通話講得仲另過廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d8b9b7019d1aab47dbd835e95ed16dd1af879a","tid":27950,"uid":10538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"